                                <h2 class="main-title text-left">
                                    <span class="bg-reverse" style="color:#000;">About Us</span>
                                </h2>
                            
                        <div class="abt-content">
                            <p style="text-align:justify;">
                                 Our Company Sachdeva Steel Products (Ship Breaking Unit) LLP and Jai Jagdish Ship Breakers Pvt. Ltd. is involved in the business since ship breaking activity started at Alang in 1983.<br /><br />

Ship breaking business was first carried out by Our Group under the name of Madhav Industrial Corporation till 1997.
In 1997, we started the business under the name Sachdeva Steel Products (Ship breakers) and till date 36 ships have been Recycled.
To further expand the business we established another unit in the year 1998 under the name of Jai Jagdish Ship Breakers Pvt. Ltd. and till date 35 ships have been Recycled.
                            </p>
                           
